        a                            capec:AttackStep ;
        capec:attackStep             "3" ;
        capec:attackStepDescription  "[Manipulate input] Once the adversary determines how to bypass filters that filter out special characters using an escaped slash, they will manipulate the user input in a way that is not intended by the application." ;
        capec:attackStepPhase        "Exploit" .

<http://w3id.org/sepses/resource/capec/ExecutionFlow/593>
        a                            capec:AttackStep ;
        capec:attackStep             "3" ;
        capec:attackStepDescription  "[Match issued IDs] The attacker brute forces different values of session ID and manages to predict a valid session ID." ;
        capec:attackStepPhase        "Experiment" ;
        capec:attackStepTechnique    "The attacker models the session ID algorithm enough to produce a compatible session IDs, or just one match." .

