        a                            capec:AttackStep ;
        capec:attackStep             "1" ;
        capec:attackStepDescription  "[Determine Application's Log File Format] The first step is exploratory meaning the attacker observes the system. The attacker looks for action and data that are likely to be logged. The attacker may be familiar with the log format of the system." ;
