<http://w3id.org/sepses/resource/capec/skillRequired/217443>
        a                        capec:SkillRequired ;
        capec:isSkillRequiredOf  capec-res:CAPEC-217 ;
        capec:skillDescription   "The adversary needs real-time access to network traffic in such a manner that the adversary can grab needed information from the SSL stream, possibly influence the decided-upon encryption method and options, and perform automated analysis to decipher encrypted material recovered. Tools exist to automate part of the tasks, but to successfully use these tools in an attack scenario requires detailed understanding of the underlying principles." ;
        capec:skillLevel         "High" .

