capec-res:CAPEC-484  a                capec:CAPEC ;
        dct:description               "This attack pattern has been deprecated as it a generalization of CAPEC-230: XML Nested Payloads and CAPEC-231: XML Oversized Payloads. Please refer to these CAPECs going forward." ;
