        capec:skillDescription   "Exploiting a buffer overflow to inject malicious code into the stack of a software system or even the heap can require a higher skill level." , "An adversary can simply overflow a buffer by inserting a long string into an adversary-modifiable injection vector. The result can be a DoS." ;
        capec:skillLevel         "High" , "Low" .

