        capec:skillDescription   "It is relatively straightforward to identify an HTTP Get method that changes state on the server side and executes against an over-privileged system interface" ;
        capec:skillLevel         "Low" .

<http://w3id.org/sepses/resource/capec/Consequence/9865>
