<http://w3id.org/sepses/resource/capec/ExecutionFlow/5611>
        a                            capec:AttackStep ;
        capec:attackStep             "1" ;
        capec:attackStepDescription  "[Acquire known Windows administrator credentials] The adversary must obtain known Windows administrator credentials in order to access the administrative network shares." ;
        capec:attackStepPhase        "Explore" ;
        capec:attackStepTechnique    "An adversary conducts a sniffing attack to steal Windows administrator credentials as they are transmitted." , "An adversary purchases breached Windows administrator credentials from the dark web." , "An adversary examines outward-facing configuration and properties files to discover hardcoded Windows administrator credentials." , "An adversary gains access to a Windows domain system/files and exfiltrates Windows administrator password hashes." , "An adversary leverages a key logger or phishing attack to steal administrator credentials as they are provided." .

