        a                            capec:AttackStep ;
        capec:attackStep             "2" ;
        capec:attackStepDescription  "[Find injection vector] The adversary identifies an injection vector to deliver the excessive content to the targeted application's buffer." ;
        capec:attackStepPhase        "Experiment" ;
        capec:attackStepTechnique    "The adversary creates or modifies a symbolic link pointing to those files which contain an excessive amount of data. If creating a symbolic link to one of those files causes different behavior in the application, then an injection vector has been identified." .

