<http://w3id.org/sepses/resource/capec/ExecutionFlow/5232>
        a                            capec:AttackStep ;
        capec:attackStep             "2" ;
        capec:attackStepDescription  "[Discover Vulnerability in Supply Chain] The adversary maps out the supply chain for the targeted system. They look for ooportunities to gain physical access to the system after it has left the manufacturer, but before it is deployed to the victim." ;
        capec:attackStepPhase        "Explore" ;
        capec:attackStepTechnique    "Procure a system and observe the steps it takes in the shipment process." , "Identify possible warehouses that systems are stored after manufacturing." .

