        a                            capec:AttackStep ;
        capec:attackStep             "3" ;
        capec:attackStepDescription  "[Craft malicious XSS URL] Once the adversary has determined which parameters are vulnerable to XSS through an error page, they will craft a malicious URL containing the XSS exploit. The adversary can have many goals, from stealing session IDs, cookies, credentials, and page content from the victim." ;
