<http://w3id.org/sepses/resource/capec/ExecutionFlow/6952>
        a                            capec:AttackStep ;
        capec:attackStep             "2" ;
        capec:attackStepDescription  "[Recreate initial repository path] The adversary re-registers the account that was renamed/deleted by the target repository's owner/maintainer and recreates the target repository with malicious code intended to exploit an application. These steps may need to happen in reverse (i.e., recreate repository and then rename an existing account to the target account) if protections are in place to prevent repository reuse." ;
