        capec:mitigation               "Implementation: use crossdomain.xml file to allow the application domain to load stuff or the SWF file called by other domain." , "Implementation: use SSL when loading external data" , "Implementation: use validation on both client and server side." , "Implementation: remove sensitive information such as user name and password in the SWF file." , "Implementation: remove debug information." ;
